\n<Alyssa><Wrap>I'm tellin' you, that skank ran over here somewhere!
\n<Nathan><Wrap>You saw that while trying to keep the blood from running out your ears, did you?
\n<Alyssa><Wrap>One of those yellin' an' screamin' Blightwalkers. She's around here somewhere.
\n<Nathan><Wrap>We woulda had her, too, if Aly here didn't run in half-cocked.
\nr<Galathan><Wrap>If you two can put the petty bickering aside, we are to escort the King to Candle Point.
\n<Thomas><Wrap>Afraid your buddy will show up for the King, Nate?
\n<Nathan><Wrap>Is there something you want to come out and say to my face, you bald fu-
\n<Thomas><Wrap>Who are you to call me bald?!
\nr<Galathan><Wrap>That's enough from both of you! We have our duty to uphold, so let's stow the bullshit and get moving.
\n<Alyssa><Wrap>Wait... Captain... You hear that? I think she's close.
\nr<Galathan><Wrap>Let's get back to \c[1]South Caembria\c[0] to retrieve the King.
